args:
The party defeats Agito, but Nedrick and the 
faeries burst onto the scene and put them at a
disadvantage. Just then, a mysterious man
arrives and defeats the restored Agito. With the
barrier nearly lifted, the prince leaves the fight
and takes off in pursuit of Nedrick and Jinlorda.
Dammit! Fightin' five'a these creeps\nat once is no joke!
Better stop with the laughing, pal,\n'cause you're next!
Forgive me! I simply could not help but\nthrill at watching you fight.
I rather think I could put the power of our\nmagic to the fullest test against you all.
Don't do this, Jinlorda! Please!\nI don't want to fight you!
We have long since passed the phase\nof discourse and reason.
To arms, everyone! Show these people\nthe true power of the faeries!
They come for us en masse!
We have no choice... Get ready, everyone!
Now let our grand melee commence,\nmy dear seventh scion!
Ah, but this rather calls to mind my sword\ntraining with Nedrick. Now have at you!
Merely amazed that faeries are possessed\nof such strength!
Nnngh... That man has such speed...
Then I will deal with him.
...I see. Even at your current age,\nit appears you are still worthy of the\nname Blazewolf.
You must be Nedrick.\nAnd it seems you're no slouch yourself.
And just how long are you all planning to\nsleep on the job? Are you not Agito?
I gave you this power, and I know it's\ncapable of so much more.
I'm glad they all finally shut up, but they're\nstill as big'a pains as ever...
Confirming an increase in enemy strength.\nThis is bad, guys! We're on our way to\nbeing at a disadvantage!
Permit me to offer my assistance.
He took down Agito! All of them!
Querying biometric data. No records found.\nIdentity unknown.\nWho could he be?
You... Just how many times do you intend\nto get in my way?
Jin, go back to the Cloudbough.\nThe barrier's almost down.
Leave this to us, King Jin! You must return\nto the upper strata!
Cut a path to our future, Your Majesty!
I am indebted to you all, and swear your\nfaith will not be wasted. ...Come, Nedrick.
We'll handle things here!\n{player_name}, do not worry.
Your Majesty, you must save Zethia!
Seventh scion, now is the time to trust\nin your comrades.
Let us continue the fight here. The enemy \nis strong, but together, we are stronger!
(How can this be?\nThere's no mistaking that visage...)
